{"id":232975703,"title":"⚠️如何預防武漢肺炎","content":"🔺注意：\n1.已經證實可以人傳人\n2.呼吸道是最容易感染的\n3.眼睛也是感染途徑\n4.少去人多的地方\n5.增強免疫力！！！\n\n🔺口罩：\n1.⭕️醫療用口罩    ❌棉口罩\n2.確實脫/戴口罩😷\n3.請遮住口鼻！！ （在路上或ig看到沒遮住的真的很想翻白眼）\nhttps://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/f7e82e4f-b660-4409-b69e-61d061c55c67/full.jpeg\n\n🔺洗手：\n1.用正確洗手方式\nhttps://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/95c109ff-4ab5-4b4f-a3d0-e71ba9ef73b2/full.jpeg\n2.不要揉眼睛 摳鼻孔\n3.沒事多洗手\n\n推薦連結：\n1.  https://youtu.be/pF4eHLObECs\n2. https://youtu.be/OCZvGUD0nO8\n\n題外話：\n預防勝於治療！！\n帶口罩➕勤洗手是保護別人更是保護自己的最佳方式\n然後希望大家多一點友善包容\n在網路上其實可以看到很多對於武漢病毒的梗圖\n縱使有多麼不喜歡中國 但生命是不分國籍的\n辛苦的永遠都是站在第一線的醫護人員\n如果送物資可以減少病毒的擴散\n也是對其他國家有那麼一點好處\n\n最重要的是口罩夠了就先不要囤貨 留給需要的人\n\n然後我玻璃心 不要罵我 \n只是不希望看到網路上一直互相謾罵 \n但卻忽略應該重視的地方","excerpt":"注意：1.已經證實可以人傳人，2.呼吸道是最容易感染的，3.眼睛也是感染途徑，4.少去人多的地方，5.增強免疫力！！！，口罩：1.⭕️醫療用口罩    棉口罩，2.確實脫/戴口罩，3.請遮住口鼻！！ ","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"fc7574ad-e1df-43d2-bb06-8825c718c065","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2020-01-29T00:55:04.953Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-29T00:55:04.953Z","commentCount":2,"likeCount":95,"tags":[],"topics":["武漢","肺炎","預防","時事"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"時事","forumAlias":"trending","school":"長庚科技大學","replyTitle":null,"gender":"F","personaSubscriptable":false,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":94},{"id":"aa0d425f-d530-4478-9a77-fe3aedc79eea","count":1}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/f7e82e4f-b660-4409-b69e-61d061c55c67/full.jpeg"},{"url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/95c109ff-4ab5-4b4f-a3d0-e71ba9ef73b2/full.jpeg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"714b81ff-2042-4842-8682-aa6ec6eb3b94","url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/f7e82e4f-b660-4409-b69e-61d061c55c67/320.jpeg","normalizedUrl":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/i